      LeonimusT<br>
      <a href="mailto:leo@leonimust.com"
        style="color: #777; text-decoration: underline;">leo@leonimust.com</a>
    </p>
    <p class="textiboi">
      We will respond to your inquiry as soon as reasonably possible.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-section animated fadeIn" style="animation-delay: 1.8s;">
    <h2 class="textiboi">Consent</h2>
    <p class="textiboi">
      By using the Package Tracking app, you acknowledge that you have read and
      understood
      this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms. You understand that your
